---
title: Southeast Asian Sweet Chilli Beef with Garlic Rice & Ginger-Soy Veggies
description: Quick-cooking beef strips are the star of this speedy Southeast Asian rice bowl. Colourful veggies including Asian greens and carrot add goodness plus a generous serve of sweet chilli sauce, lemon and soy sauce combine into a sweet and savoury dish that'll be a hit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southeast-asian-sweet-chilli-beef-d09fac72.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/southeast-asian-sweet-chilli-beef-5f34e13d8b613f4d654a9122-cc4c70df.pdf
